== Code used (license obligations apply) ==

- gavagai (https://github.com/hinanohart/gavagai), MIT License
  Used: HookedSAEBundle type adapter (decoder/encoder shape convention)
  in polyalign/backends/gavagai_bridge.py. The gavagai pairwise
  indeterminacy score (gavagai.score.gavagai_score) is NOT invoked in
  v0.1.0a1 / v0.1.0a2; score integration is deferred to v0.1.1.

- recurrentlens (https://github.com/hinanohart/recurrentlens), MIT License
